<title>BELGIUM: BMT-Groep H1 pre-tax up 23.7 pct.</title>
<headline>BMT-Groep H1 pre-tax up 23.7 pct.</headline>
<dateline>BRUSSELS 1996-08-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months to June 30, 1996</p>
<p>(in millions of Belgian francs unless stated)</p>
<p>    Pre-tax profit			249.5  vs   201.7</p>
<p>    Turnover			    2,842    vs 2,650</p>
<p>    Gross cash flow		     429.5  vs   391.1</p>
<p>    Depreciations			 156.9  vs   165.4</p>
<p>    Goodwill write-offs		  23.1  vs    24.0.</p>
<p>NOTE - BMT-Groep, a Belgian metals group, said it expected turnover to rise slightly and gross cash flow to remain steady in the current year. First-half results rose on the back of cost control, an improved margin and slightly lower depreciations.</p>
<p>-- Brussels Newsroom +32 2 287 6810, Fax +32 2 230 7710</p>
